  <text xml:id="t1">
    <body xml:id="t1-body">      
      <pb n="1" facs="#rb054a" xml:id="t1-body-pb1"/> 
      <opener>
        <dateline>
          <name type="place" ref="#LEM" key="LEM">Lemnos</name>
          <lb/>
          <date when="1915-11-02">2 Nov 1915</date>
        </dateline>
        <lb/>
        <salute>Beaut old thing:</salute>
      </opener>      
      <p>        
        Have just dis-
        <lb/>
        covered a photograph
        <lb/>
        taken at <name type="place" ref="#CYP" key="CYP">Cyprus</name> - it was
        <lb/>
        part of a group not
        <lb/>
        interesting so I cut
        <lb/>
        it out thinking you
        <lb/>
        might like to have it.
      </p>
      
      <p>        
        The sun was in my
        <lb/>
        eyes so it is rather
        <lb/>
        screwed up. You will
        <lb/>
        notice that I an not 
        <lb/>
        looking very ill.
      </p>
      
      <pb n="2" facs="#rb054b" xml:id="t1-body-pb2"/>
      
      <p>
        I am glad to hear
        <lb/>
        <name type="person" ref="#NIC" key="NIC">Nicholls</name>is coming at
        <lb/>
        last, he will be 
        <lb/>
        joyful. Remember me
        <lb/>
        to them when you
        <lb/>
        see them.</p>      
      
      <closer>
        <salute>
          Good night
          <lb/>
          sweetheart
        </salute>
        <lb/>        
        <signed><name type="person" ref="#RTB" key="RTB">Roy</name></signed>
      </closer>      
    </body>
  </text>
